@startuml
title Homotopy Regressors - Arquitectura de Componentes

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Core Escalar" {
  [solver.py] as Solver
  [regressor.py] as Regressor
  [derivatives.py] as Derivatives
  [parser.py] as Parser
}

package "Core Sistemas" {
  [solver_system.py] as SolverSys
  [regressor_system.py] as RegressorSys
}

package "Validacion e Identificacion" {
  [verify_regressor.py] as Verify
  [identify_parameters.py] as Identify
}

package "Scripts y Tests" {
  [examples.py] as Examples
  [test_regressor_vs_rk4.py] as TestRK
  [test_inverse_regressor.py] as TestInv
}

Regressor --> Solver : genera callables\nf,df,d2f,d3f
Parser --> Regressor : parsea EDO\nforma estandar
Derivatives --> Solver : utilidades discretas

RegressorSys --> SolverSys : funcs/jac/hess/tensor\nsymbolic -> numeric

Verify --> Regressor : compara salida HAM
Verify --> RegressorSys : compara salida HAM
Identify --> Regressor : usa mismos stencils 3 puntos

Examples --> Regressor
Examples --> Solver
TestRK --> Verify
TestInv --> Regressor

@enduml
